text: "With My Own Eyes" is a 2000 song by the German DJ group Sash! and it features Finnish singer Inka Auhagen. It is the third single from Sash's third studio album Trilenium which was released on 22 May 2000. ==Charts== ===Weekly charts=== Chart (2000) Peak position Europe (Eurochart Hot 100) 41 Romania (Romanian Top 100) 5 ===Year- end charts=== Chart (2000) Position Romania (Romanian Top 100) 49 ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Sash! songs
